#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Tips for Success<br/><br/></span></strong>"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: Automate invoices, reconcile payments, and "
"track profitability per tour type"
msgstr ""
"<strong>會計</strong>：自動產生發票、對賬付款記錄，以及追蹤各種導賞團的盈利能"
"力"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Activate the multilingual website setting to localize your website "
"to international audiences.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>啟動「多語言」網站設定，讓公司網站能面向全球受眾，提供國際化內容。</"
"strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Antwerp</strong> dazzles with its fashion-forward spirit and rich "
"artistic heritage. Explore the legacy of Rubens, marvel at the gothic "
"Cathedral of Our Lady, and stroll through the dynamic streets of this port "
"city where tradition meets modern creativity."
msgstr ""
"<strong>安特衛普</strong>以前衛的時尚精神及豐富的藝術文化底蘊，教人驚艷又着"
"迷。探索魯本斯的藝術遺產，欣賞哥德式聖母大教堂的宏偉壯觀，在這座港口城市充滿"
"活力氣氛的大街小巷漫步，感受傳統與現代創意完美融合的結晶品。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Appointments</strong>: Allow customers to book private tours based "
"on availability and language preferences."
msgstr ""
"<strong>預約</strong>：讓客戶可根據剩餘名額情況及語言偏好等，自行預訂私人導賞"
"團。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Apps &amp; What They Do:</strong>"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Brussels</strong>, the heart of Europe, welcomes you with grand "
"architecture, cobblestone streets, and a vibrant atmosphere. From the "
"opulent Grand Place to the surreal world of Magritte, this city is a must-"
"see for culture lovers and history buffs alike."
msgstr ""
"<strong>布魯塞爾</strong>是歐洲的中心，以宏偉建築、鵝卵石鋪滿的街道，以及充滿"
"活力的氣氛迎接你。從富麗堂皇的市集大廣場，到馬格里特畫筆下的超現實世界，這座"
"城市是文化愛好者及歷史迷的必遊之地。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create services</strong> for each destination &amp; language pair"
msgstr "為不同目的地及導賞語言組合，<strong>建立專屬服務</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create visually rich pages</strong> with images, videos, and tour "
"descriptions"
msgstr ""
"加入圖片、影片及文字，介紹旅遊團詳情，<strong>建立視覺效果豐富又吸引的網頁</"
"strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Customers book online</strong> and receive <strong>automated "
"reminders</strong>"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Customize layouts easily</strong> using drag-and-drop editor"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Dashboards</strong>: Visualize your KPIs—bookings per guide, top-"
"selling tours, revenue trends"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Dashboard 概覽畫面</strong>：將你的關鍵績效指標 KPI 以視覺形式呈現，"
"公司營運狀況一目了然，包括不同導遊的預訂數量、最暢銷的行程路線、整體收入趨勢"
"等"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Define each tour</strong> as an event with time slots and capacities"
msgstr ""
"<strong>可將每種導賞團設為一個活動</strong>，並設立不同時段及參加人數上限。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Define guide availability</strong> per service"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Digital tickets with QR codes</strong> for easy on-site check-in"
msgstr "使用<strong>二維碼電子門票</strong>，方便現場登記出席。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Enable online booking &amp; payment</strong>, no manual follow-up "
"needed"
msgstr "<strong>啟用線上預訂及付款功能</strong>，無需人手處理"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Events</strong>: Set up group tours with schedules and manage "
"bookings and attendance."
msgstr ""
"<strong>活動</strong>：設定團體旅遊，提供行程及時間表等資訊，管理預約及出席情"
"況。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Ghent</strong> enchants with medieval splendor and a youthful "
"energy. Discover castles, canals, and hidden alleyways as you uncover the "
"soul of a city where past and present coexist in perfect harmony."
msgstr ""
"<strong>根特</strong>最令人着迷的，是它在中世紀的輝煌歷史，以及現代的青春活"
"力。探索宏偉城堡、壯麗運河，以及隱世的小巷，發掘這座城市的獨有靈魂，感受新舊"
"世界完美融合的魅力。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
msgid ""
"<strong>Ghent</strong> is the kind of city that sneaks up on you — and "
"steals your heart. A vibrant mix of gothic spires, canalside charm, artistic "
"rebellion, and youthful energy, Ghent is one of Belgium’s best-kept secrets… "
"though the word is definitely getting out."
msgstr ""
"<strong>根特</strong>是那種低調、悄悄吸引你，最後緊緊鎖住你心的城市。根特市融"
"合哥德式尖頂建築、運河流域風情、反叛活潑的藝術及青春活力，多姿多彩，是比利時"
"其中一處最不為人知的隱世秘境⋯⋯不過，它的名聲也開始逐漸傳揚開去了。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Handle walk-in traffic</strong> efficiently with synced stock"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid "<strong>Included</strong>"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Integrate booking buttons</strong> directly with group or private "
"tour modules"
msgstr "<strong>將預訂按鈕直接整合</strong>至團體或私人導賞團的模組內"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3841
msgid "<strong>Join Our Guided Group Tours — Discover More Together</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>參加我們的導賞團，一起探索更多精彩</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Namur</strong>, nestled at the confluence of the Meuse and Sambre "
"rivers, invites you to slow down and savor the beauty of Wallonia. Its "
"imposing citadel, relaxed charm, and panoramic views make it a serene yet "
"fascinating stop on your Belgian adventure."
msgstr ""
"<strong>那慕爾</strong>坐落在默茲河與桑布爾河的交匯處，邀請你放慢腳步，細心品"
"味瓦隆尼亞的美麗。這座城市的宏偉城堡、悠閒氣氛及環迴全景景觀，將會是你比利時"
"之旅中，恬靜而迷人的一站。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid "<strong>Not included</strong>"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Open POS session</strong> and view tour availabilities"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Optimize SEO</strong> to attract tourists searching online"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid "<strong>Our offering</strong><br>"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Point of Sale</strong>: Sell tickets in person, print receipts, and "
"manage real-time tour availabilities."
msgstr ""
"<strong>POS 銷售點管理</strong>：現場售票、列印收據、實時管理導賞團剩餘名額"
"等。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Print receipts</strong> with booking details"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Recruitment</strong>: Manage applications and onboarding for new "
"tour guides"
msgstr "<strong>招聘</strong>：管理新導遊的職位申請及入職流程"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Regularly update website content</strong> with new tours, seasonal "
"offerings, and high-quality visuals"
msgstr ""
"<strong>定期更新網站內容</strong>，包括介紹新的導賞團及行程路線，加入節慶優"
"惠、高解像度壯麗照片等。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Reminders &amp; confirmation emails</strong> reduce no-shows"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Sell remaining spots</strong> for today’s tours or future ones"
msgstr "<strong>銷售即日或未來導賞團的剩餘名額</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Marketing</strong>: Schedule and post on social media to "
"boost tour visibility"
msgstr ""
"<strong>社交媒體推廣</strong>：編排發文時間，自動在社交媒體發佈內容，提高公司"
"的網上曝光率。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Surveys</strong>: Gather guest feedback after each tour to "
"continuously improve"
msgstr ""
"<strong>網上調查</strong>：每次遊覽結束後，都收集遊客的回應及意見，持續改進"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Track attendance live</strong> from a mobile device or the "
"attendances app"
msgstr ""
"可透過手機、流動裝置或考勤應用程式，<strong>實時追蹤參加者出席情況</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Train staff</strong> on using POS for quick ticketing"
msgstr "<strong>訓練職員使用 POS 機</strong>，快速出票售票"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use QR check-ins</strong> to save time and reduce human error"
msgstr "<strong>使用二維碼簽到</strong>，節省時間，減少人為錯誤"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Use automated emails</strong> to remind customers of their upcoming "
"tours"
msgstr "<strong>利用自動化電子郵件</strong>，在導賞團舉行前提醒客戶"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Use dashboards:</strong> Track key metrics like most popular cities "
"and languages"
msgstr ""
"<strong>使用 Dashboard 概覽畫面</strong>：追蹤關鍵的統計指標，例如最熱門城"
"市、最多人選擇的語言等"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Website</strong>: Build attractive pages to present your tours and "
"convert visitors into customers."
msgstr ""
