#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
msgid ""
"Nestled at the meeting point of the Meuse and Sambre rivers, <strong>Namur "
"is a city that whispers stories of centuries past while buzzing with the "
"energy of modern Wallonia.</strong> Once a medieval stronghold and now the "
"capital of the region, Namur offers a rich tapestry of history, culture, "
"architecture, and natural beauty. And there’s no better way to discover it "
"all than from the comfort of a guided bus tour designed to show you both the "
"highlights and the hidden gems."
msgstr ""
"那慕爾坐落在默茲河與桑布爾河的交匯處，這座城市<strong>散發着幾個世紀以來的歷"
"史韻味，又充滿活力，洋溢現代瓦隆尼亞的朝氣</strong>。那慕爾曾是中世紀的要塞，"
"如今是該區首府，擁有豐富的歷史、文化、建築及自然美景。要探索這座城市，最好的"
"方式莫過於參加舒適的巴士觀光遊，帶你欣賞它的奪目景色，以及鮮為人知的隱世寶"
"藏。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo Point of Sale is optimized for mobile usage. Use it on the go to take "
"last minute bookings if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Odoo POS 銷售點管理系統，針對流動裝置調整，適合手機使用。如有需要，更可在外出"
"期間，隨時隨地處理臨時預訂。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo Website lets you build an appealing online presence to showcase your "
"guided tours."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 網站製作工具，協助你建立吸引人的線上形象，展示各種遊覽及導賞團服務。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo empowers guided tour businesses by centralizing operations, automating "
"bookings, and creating beautiful customer experiences."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 透過集中營運流程、自動化預訂，以及創造美好的客戶體驗，協助你提升導遊業務"
"水平。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo.com/trial"
msgstr "Odoo.com/trial"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "On-Site Ticket Sales 🧾"
msgstr ""

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once your core operations are running smoothly, consider expanding your "
"toolset:"
msgstr "核心業務開始流暢運作後，便可考慮擴展工具套裝："

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"Our <strong>Antwerp Discovery Bus Tour</strong> invites you to explore the "
"many layers of this fascinating city, from its medieval heart to its modern "
"edge. Glide past the towering Cathedral of Our Lady and the vibrant Grote "
"Markt, admire the intricate guild houses, and learn how a 16th-century port "
"grew into one of the world’s diamond capitals."
msgstr ""
"我們的「<strong>安特衛普巴士探索之旅</strong>」誠邀你深入了解這座迷人的城市，"
"揭開層層內涵，由中世紀的市中心，走到現代化的新發展區。巴士會帶你途經高聳入雲"
"的聖母大教堂，以及車水馬龍、人潮如鯽的大市集，欣賞精緻的議會建築，了解這座 "
"16 世紀的港口城市，如何逐步發展成世界其中一個鑽石之都。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
msgid ""
"Our <strong>Brussels Explorer Tour</strong> takes you on a rich and varied "
"ride through the city's many faces — from the grandeur of the Royal Palace "
"to the modern glass towers of the European Quarter, from medieval alleyways "
"near the Grand-Place to the sprawling beauty of Cinquantenaire Park."
msgstr ""
"我們的<strong>布魯塞爾探索之旅</strong>，會帶你欣賞這座城市豐富多彩的風貌：從"
"宏偉的皇室宮殿，到歐洲區的現代化玻璃幕牆大樓，以至大市集廣場附近的中世紀懷舊"
"小巷，還有獨立革命五十週年紀念公園的壯闊景色。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
msgid ""
"Our <strong>Ghent Highlights Bus Tour</strong> gives you a front-row seat to "
"this city’s rich past and dynamic present. From the imposing Castle of the "
"Counts to the shimmering St. Bavo’s Cathedral, from the industrial docklands "
"reborn into cultural hubs to student-filled squares echoing with laughter "
"and debate — Ghent is full of contrast, and endlessly fascinating."
msgstr ""
"我們的<strong>根特市精華巴士遊</strong>，會帶你近距離感受這座城市的豐富歷史，"
"以及現今的活力繁華。從宏偉的伯爵城堡，到閃閃生輝的聖巴夫大教堂；從舊工業碼頭"
"改建重生的文藝氣息區域，以至學生喜愛流連、充滿歡笑聲及激烈辯論的廣場，根特都"
"充滿精彩而強烈的對比，教人着迷。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
msgid ""
"Our <strong>Namur Discovery Tour</strong> invites you to sit back, relax, "
"and enjoy a panoramic journey through the city’s most iconic sites and "
"neighborhoods. Whether you're just visiting for the day or want to deepen "
"your understanding of this fascinating city, our professional guide will "
"bring Namur to life with engaging commentary, local anecdotes, and "
"surprising facts."
msgstr ""
"我們的<strong>發現那慕爾之旅</strong>，是你放鬆身心，環迴飽覽全市景觀之選，帶"
"你欣賞最具代表性的地標及社區。無論你只是一日遊，還是想深入探索這座迷人城市，"
"我們的專業導遊都會以生動的講解、當地趣聞，以及令人意想不到的冷知識，帶你認識"
"那慕爾最真實一面。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_4
msgid ""
"Our company specializes in consulting, product development, and customer "
"support. We tailor our services to fit the unique needs of businesses across "
"various sectors, helping them grow and succeed in a competitive market."
msgstr ""
"我們公司專注提供諮詢、產品開發，以及客戶支援服務。我們會根據各行各業的獨特需"
"求，為企業度身設計服務，幫助他們在競爭激烈的市場中增長及取得成功。"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
msgid ""
"Our guide will take you beyond the guidebook, sharing tales of medieval "
"merchants, revolutionary thinkers, and contemporary innovators. You'll "
"cruise past stunning architecture, lively street art, tranquil rivers, and "
"bustling markets — all from the comfort of a modern coach with regular stops "
"for photos and exploration."
msgstr ""
"我們的導遊會帶你細看旅遊書籍不會提及的精彩地方，講述中世紀商人、革命思想家及"
"當代創新人士的故事。你會乘坐舒適的現代化旅遊巴士，沿途欣賞令人嘆為觀止的建"
"築、充滿活力的街頭藝術、恬靜悠閒的河流景緻，以及熙來攘往的熱鬧市集。巴士會定"
"期停車或停站，方便你拍照及下車探索。"

